# Non-ASCII filename source images — kept locally but must not be tracked,
# because GitHub Pages' actions/checkout step has been failing on them
# (all Pages deploys starting at commit 50ba0d4 crashed at the checkout
# step). The actually-served avatar assets live under assets/avatar/ with
# ASCII names (pink-portrait.png, pink-awake.png).
粉色头像.png
粉色女生_00000_iSpt.png

# tts-server/ is a separate local project with its own .git repo.
# It was accidentally tracked as a dangling git submodule (gitlink
# mode 160000, no .gitmodules entry), which made GitHub Pages'
# actions/checkout step fail on every deploy. Keeping it as an
# ignored sibling directory so local TTS dev is unaffected.
tts-server/
